      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty in person. Honestly, I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a single blemish on it, and the interior is absolutely spotless. It drives like an absolute dream\u2014smooth, quiet, and super responsive. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know someone is going to be so happy behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
