      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is a pristine 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the high-revving 13B-REW twin-sequential turbocharged rotary engine. This specimen boasts exceptional compression across all rotor faces and a perfectly synchronized turbo transition. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen LSD, ensuring optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. The lightweight chassis retains its original 50/50 weight distribution and double-wishbone suspension geometry, offering unparalleled tactile feedback. Meticulously maintained with a documented vacuum-line refresh and cooling system upgrade, this FD remains in its factory-delivered state with no modifications or structural wear. A true turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
